headline: MSC Industrial (MSM) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: MSC Industrial (MSM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 17.81% and 2.59%, respectively, for the quarter ended November 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
